      "content": "but finding the \"right people\" feels like a fantasy. i've tried so hard and it never works. it's like i'm speaking a different language than everyone else. sometimes i just think... what if there is no version of this where i actually feel at peace? what if the only way to stop the noise and the exhaustion is to just... stop?",
